  .container-fluid
    main(role='main')
        .jumbotron
            h1
               | A College-Level Introduction to Computing Using Java
            p.lead
                | Through this course, students will learn the material of a typical  introductory computer science course at leading universities and will have the background for the AP Computer Science A exam.
            .row
                .col-md-auto
                    p
                      span.font-weight-bold.text-success Timing 
                      | Saturdays, 10:00 AM - 12:10 PM
                .col-md-auto
                    p
                      span.font-weight-bold.text-success Prerequisite  
                      | 1 year of experience with python, Java, or a similar language
                .col-md-auto
                    p
                      span.font-weight-bold.text-success Cost 
                      | $800/student 
